title: Lal Baadshah
subTitle: Lal Singh, a righteous and helpful man, clashes against Dayal Singh, a powerful personality. However, things get complicated when a hidden treasure is involved and Lal's tragic past is disclosed.

title: Kabzaa
subTitle: Ravi works for Veljibhai Soda, a gangster, and does illegal work for him. Once, he is asked to vacate Ali from his property, but he gets inspired by his ideals and decides to change his ways.

title: Fox
subTitle: Arjun, an accomplished but corrupt criminal lawyer who has the habit of winning each case he fights, decides to turn over a new leaf. However, soon he is accused of killing five people.

title: Khoj
subTitle: Ravi and Anita's vacation turns into a nightmare when Anita vanishes without a trace. Ravi's frantic search leads to more questions than answers when a woman appears, claiming to be his missing wife.

title: I Killed Bapu
subTitle: Nathuram Godse becomes one of the most hated men in the country after he assassinates Mahatma Gandhi. When he has his day in court, he explains his thoughts and motivations behind the crime.

title: Filler
subTitle: Bringing the best in television.

title: Daraar
subTitle: Raj Malhotra, a wealthy man, falls for Priya. However, things get complicated when Vikram, Priya's abusive husband, enters the frame.

title: Krack
subTitle: Veera Shankar, a hot headed police sergeant, forms a vicious rivalry with notorious crime figure, Katari Krishna.

title: Ek Rishtaa: The Bond of Love
subTitle: Amid the ideological differences with his father Vijay, Ajay steps up to protect his family from Rajesh's, his brother-in-law's, evil intentions.

title: Entertainment
subTitle: Akhil, an underdog and a failure, comes to know that his real father is a rich diamond merchant who has just passed away. When he goes to retrieve his wealth, he learns that a dog has inherited it.

title: Dacait
subTitle: After being mercilessly beaten and abandoned to die, a young man is rescued by a band of dacoits, who nurse him back to health in their hidden lair.

title: Paappi Devataa
subTitle: Ram and Rahim become best friends after the latter offers shelter to Ram when he comes to Bombay. However, Ram is unaware that Rahim is involved in illegal activities.

title: Mera Dost Ghatothkach
subTitle: A girl and her caretaker kaka's life changes when Ghatotkach and a robot enter their world after Kaka's death, leading to exciting adventures.

title: Hum Intezaar Karenge
subTitle: Manisha, a wealthy woman, falls in love with Ajay, a middle-class man, who promises to marry her and settle down within three years. However, after the time period passes, he mysteriously disappears.

title: Tez Dhaar
subTitle: Two women, Rekha and Nandini, are on the run for their lives after they get involved in a tussle with Perriayyah and accidentally end up killing him.

title: Jai Shree Ganesh
subTitle: Revered as the god of good luck, Lord Ganesh returns to the world to grant good fortune to the living and relieve pain and misery among devotees.

title: Ek Aur Ek Gyarah
subTitle: Tara and Sitara, siblings and small-time con-men, are on the run from a wanted criminal after they accidentally shoot at him. Soon they end up at the house of major Ram Singh, where they take refuge.

title: Dosti: Friends Forever
subTitle: Karan, a wealthy heir, lives a lonely life and is neglected by his family. When he has a fatal accident, Raj, a poor orphan, saves his life and they become inseparable friends.

title: Naseeb Apna Apna
subTitle: A naive village girl marries the son of a domineering man. However, upon her arrival at his house in the city, she finds out that he is already married.

title: Mard
subTitle: Azad, a wealthy prosperous king, is locked in a dungeon by General Dyer who wants to take over his kingdom. Years later, Azad's son comes to his father's rescue and puts an end to Dyer's tyranny.

title: Jawan
subTitle: Driven by a personal vendetta, a man sets out to rectify the wrongs in the society to keep a promise made years ago.

title: Military Raaj
subTitle: Major Anand is reassigned to a camp for unruly cadets but soon finds himself confronting deeper threats as lawlessness rises and the authorities struggle to maintain order.

title: Bacho Ke Sakha Bhagwan
subTitle: Children venture out on a pilgrimage and visit several holy shrines devoted to different gods, so that they can please them and ask for their help.

title: Padmanabham Temple - Hidden Secret
subTitle: After temple thefts and a journalist's death while probing Sree Padmanabhaswamy temple's defenses, Aditya investigates the mysterious events.

title: Aranya
subTitle: Devastated by a minister's plans to raze a thriving forest and turn it into an urban settlement, a lone man decides to protect the jungle and its residents.

title: Teri Meherbaniyan
subTitle: Ram, an honest man, falls in love with a woman named Bijli and goes on to help the people of her village. However, the region's corrupt leader, Thakur Vijay Singh, soon begins to plot against him.

title: Toofan
subTitle: Separated at birth, the paths of Shyam, a lousy magician unwittingly roped into a crime, and Toofan, a defender of the people, cross again years later as they reunite to avenge their father.

title: Kishen Kanhaiya
subTitle: Separated at birth, Kishen and Kanhaiya grow up in different worlds, one in opulent luxury, the other in poverty. Fate reunites them as they fight together to end injustice.

title: Rathnam
subTitle: After Malliga is harassed by a notorious land grabber and his brothers, Rathnam, a subordinate of an influential politician, protects her from their attacks.

title: Jaanwar
subTitle: A criminal changes the course of his life when he decides to raise a baby who has survived a train crash, but chaos ensues when his past begins to haunt him.

title: Encounter Shankar
subTitle: Post his transfer to a village, an encounter specialist sets out to stop a crime boss who wants to build a power plant in the region despite strong public opposition.
